  "body": "# Bug Report\n\n## Problem\nWhen enter recipient address or scanning valid QR on \"Send transaction\"  screen focus for a moment is set on amount field  (so the keyboard is opened, and then it is hidden)\n\n#### Expected behavior\nKeyboard is not hidden\n\n#### Actual behavior\nKeyboard appears for a moment and hides\n![ezgif com-video-to-gif (3)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/77064528-eba05c00-69df-11ea-9148-5ba6d28cb63a.gif)\n\n\n#### Notes\n\nFor the developer who will be investigating. Is it related to another PR? Tips on where to start? \n\n\n### Reproduction\n\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\n\n- Open Status > Wallet\n- Tap on Send transaction\n- Choose > Scan QR in \"Choose recipient\"\n- Scan valid QR\n\n### Additional Information\n\n- Status version: nightly 19/03/2019\n- Operating System: Android, iOS",
